1
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:07,920
Jiang Xun is the only one

2
00:01:08,760 --> 00:01:10,439
who knows the key.

3
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:12,959
We must catch her alive.

4
00:01:12,959 --> 00:01:14,079
But she...

5
00:01:14,519 --> 00:01:15,319
She...

6
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:18,079
She was thrown into the sea by Shen Shutu.

7
00:01:18,079 --> 00:01:18,959
She's not dead.

8
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:22,560
She's in the safe house in Harbor City.

9
00:01:23,359 --> 00:01:24,560
Safe house?

10
00:01:26,040 --> 00:01:27,280
The situation there is unclear.

11
00:01:27,319 --> 00:01:28,159
I can't get in.

12
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:30,640
I can only arrange guards there.

13
00:01:39,959 --> 00:01:41,280
To draw us away,

14
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:43,159
he put on a good show for me.

15
00:01:44,159 --> 00:01:45,120
Good.

16
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:46,120
Very good.

17
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:48,239
I used to call you dumb.

18
00:01:49,319 --> 00:01:51,079
I didn't expect that I was also fooled

19
00:01:51,079 --> 00:01:52,760
by them.

20
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:56,400
Shen Shutu.

21
00:01:57,239 --> 00:01:58,120
Jiang Xun.

22
00:01:58,719 --> 00:02:00,159
You just wait.

23
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:10,919
Bro,

24
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,680
no one's been here all day.

25
00:02:14,159 --> 00:02:15,960
What are they doing over there?

26
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,120
Just do your job.

27
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:18,680
Cut the crap.

28
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:43,199
I'm almost winning. Just one tile away.

29
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,520
How can you be sure

30
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:46,199
the tile is under the pile

31
00:02:46,199 --> 00:02:47,520
instead of in the opponent's hand?

32
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:48,560
Shen Shutu,

33
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,120
don't worry about me.

34
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,599
You win first.

35
00:02:52,879 --> 00:02:54,120
What about you?

36
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:54,919
Just like this?

37
00:03:04,479 --> 00:03:05,639
Still playing games?

38
00:03:09,319 --> 00:03:10,960
Why are they staring outside for so long?

39
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,639
Ke Yu'ang and the others finally

40
00:03:12,639 --> 00:03:13,960
found out where we are.

41
00:03:14,159 --> 00:03:15,759
They definitely won't leave easily.

42
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:18,319
Why are they so fixated on the jade pendant?

43
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,960
Who tied it must untie it.

44
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:25,319
I want to go to Great-Grandmother's former residence.

45
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:27,639
Maybe we can find some clues.

46
00:03:44,759 --> 00:03:45,840
Are those people

47
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:46,919
your "White Moonlight"?

48
00:03:47,159 --> 00:03:48,360
White Moonlight?

49
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,159
It's Black Moonlight.

50
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:52,159
They can kill us at any time.

51
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,159
Are you afraid?

52
00:03:54,319 --> 00:03:55,879
With you here, I'm not afraid at all.

53
00:03:58,080 --> 00:04:00,080
Then why do they just stand outside?

54
00:04:01,159 --> 00:04:02,719
Because this is a safe house.

55
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:04,199
It has an emergency alarm system inside.

56
00:04:04,199 --> 00:04:05,120
They dare not break in.

57
00:04:06,159 --> 00:04:07,759
But if we go out,

58
00:04:07,759 --> 00:04:08,599
it's hard to say.

59
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,000
Then

60
00:04:10,159 --> 00:04:11,560
let's go inside quickly.

61
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,159
Shh.

62
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:30,160
Great-Grandma is a taciturn person.

63
00:04:30,959 --> 00:04:32,480
After she raised Grandpa,

64
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,879
she moved out on her own.

65
00:04:34,439 --> 00:04:36,560
She wasn't that close to my dad.

66
00:04:37,319 --> 00:04:38,759
In my memory,

67
00:04:39,079 --> 00:04:42,319
she's a tough old lady.

68
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,839
After she moved back to Harbor City,

69
00:04:46,839 --> 00:04:48,319
she worked as a tutor

70
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,480
and a translator.

71
00:04:49,959 --> 00:04:52,279
Many young talents have wooed her,

72
00:04:52,439 --> 00:04:53,519
but she never remarried.

73
00:04:54,639 --> 00:04:55,839
I remember

74
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:58,519
she kept looking at this box before she died.

75
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,600
This box

76
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:06,040
seems to have been preserved for a long time.

77
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,720
Is there something valuable inside?

78
00:05:09,199 --> 00:05:10,399
I don't know.

79
00:05:10,399 --> 00:05:11,680
I was too young at that time.

80
00:05:12,079 --> 00:05:13,360
I've never opened it.

81
00:05:30,759 --> 00:05:32,240
These are all Great-Grandmother's accessories.

82
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,680
Great-Grandmother's diary.

83
00:06:05,759 --> 00:06:06,759
You really

84
00:06:08,879 --> 00:06:10,319
look like your Great-Grandfather.

85
00:06:10,319 --> 00:06:12,240
You look exactly like your Great-Grandmother.

86
00:06:17,839 --> 00:06:18,639
Wow.

87
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,040
This

88
00:06:28,399 --> 00:06:30,439
is the torn photo

89
00:06:30,439 --> 00:06:31,720
when they quarreled.

90
00:06:41,959 --> 00:06:42,759
What's wrong?

91
00:06:43,959 --> 00:06:45,160
Why are you so sad?

92
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,480
Because I suddenly understand

93
00:06:54,519 --> 00:06:56,639
that Great-Grandma is definitely not a traitor.

94
00:06:56,639 --> 00:06:58,240
They hid their identities

95
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:00,839
just for the sake of the nation.

96
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:03,279
If there was no war,

97
00:07:03,759 --> 00:07:05,120
would they be

98
00:07:05,439 --> 00:07:07,040
a couple for the ages,

99
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:09,519
with a big family

100
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,240
and a life of joy?

101
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,279
Maybe

102
00:07:18,199 --> 00:07:19,720
their story

103
00:07:20,439 --> 00:07:21,600
can be continued

104
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,279
by us.

105
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:36,759
No matter what happens in the future,

106
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,680
whether the road ahead

107
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:40,160
is smooth or full of thorns,

108
00:07:41,279 --> 00:07:42,759
I want to hold your hand

109
00:07:43,319 --> 00:07:44,920
and protect you.

110
00:07:52,759 --> 00:07:53,720
So,

111
00:07:55,759 --> 00:07:56,839
Ms Jiang Xun,

112
00:08:00,759 --> 00:08:01,879
will you

113
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:05,279
marry Mr Shen Shutu?

114
00:08:10,879 --> 00:08:11,759
I haven't bought the ring yet.

115
00:08:11,759 --> 00:08:12,759
I'll make it up later.

116
00:08:32,519 --> 00:08:33,360
Yes, I will.

117
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:35,159
You said yes?

118
00:08:35,279 --> 00:08:35,879
Yeah.

119
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:02,320
She's asleep.

120
00:09:04,279 --> 00:09:05,759
Then get in quickly.

121
00:09:05,759 --> 00:09:06,519
It's okay.

122
00:09:07,279 --> 00:09:08,159
Take your time.

123
00:09:08,159 --> 00:09:08,559
Come on.

124
00:09:18,279 --> 00:09:20,399
A cryptographic key makes you so hard.

125
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:23,440
You'd better buy a grave and die in it.

126
00:09:26,799 --> 00:09:29,720
Boss, we've reviewed the video of the block today.

127
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:31,759
We found Jiang Xun and Shen Shutu

128
00:09:31,759 --> 00:09:32,840
left the safe house.

129
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:35,720
They also went to the place where Jiang Xun's great-grandmother lived.

130
00:09:35,919 --> 00:09:38,279
These are some old stories about Jiang family.

131
00:10:02,919 --> 00:10:04,639
So the descendant of a hero

132
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,919
is also the descendant of a traitor.

133
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,600
Contact the media

134
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:11,600
and put Jiang's scandal on the hot search.

135
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,559
I want to burn this fire

136
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:15,679
to Rongzhou immediately.

137
00:10:16,399 --> 00:10:17,200
Yes.

138
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:19,399
Jiang Xun,

139
00:10:19,879 --> 00:10:21,080
you are always against me.

140
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:22,279
It's time for you to suffer.

141
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:24,440
The Shen Family

142
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:28,000
will never accept you, a traitor's offspring.

143
00:10:59,039 --> 00:11:01,240
[Shen Shutu knelt on one knee to propose,]

144
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:03,360
[giving his lifelong commitment to his beloved,]

145
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:06,039
[yet still harboring an unfinished mission.]

146
00:11:06,159 --> 00:11:08,519
[Song Jin'an, with deep affection for his homeland,]

147
00:11:08,639 --> 00:11:10,159
[clinging to his obsession with his lover,]

148
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:11,840
[endured criticism]

149
00:11:11,879 --> 00:11:13,360
[and moved forward with dignity.]

150
00:11:13,519 --> 00:11:15,720
[This is the true portrayal of the covert front.]

151
00:11:15,759 --> 00:11:17,919
[When the country and people needed them,]

152
00:11:17,919 --> 00:11:20,360
[they always put the collective before the individual,]

153
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:21,559
[always ready]

154
00:11:21,679 --> 00:11:22,679
[to rush to the front line]

155
00:11:22,679 --> 00:11:24,399
[to safeguard national security]

156
00:11:24,399 --> 00:11:25,919
[and the interests of the people without hesitation.]

157
00:11:26,559 --> 00:11:29,320
[They buried their debt to their families deep in their hearts,]

158
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:31,759
[and the prosperity and peace of the country]

159
00:11:31,759 --> 00:11:33,440
[were their most affectionate consolation]

160
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:34,840
[to their loved ones,]

161
00:11:35,399 --> 00:11:37,759
[and the most resolute response to their original aspirations.]
